@startuml
participant UI as "SubscriptionSection"
participant Provider as "subscriptionProvider"
participant Repo as "BillingRepository"
participant DB as "Supabase (Table)"

UI -> Provider: ref.watch(subscriptionProvider)
activate Provider
Provider -> Repo: fetchSubscription()
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: Select from user_subscriptions (RLS)
activate DB
DB --> Repo: JSON Data
deactivate DB
Repo --> Provider: Subscription (Domain Model)
deactivate Repo
Provider --> UI: AsyncValue<Subscription>
deactivate Provider

UI -> UI: Render Status & Plan
@enduml
